A wyvern rider of Daein. Only daughter of
Shiharam Fizzart, lord of Talrega. Appears
in Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance.

A girl whose constant hunger pangs cause
stress for her and worry for others. Has a
seemingly bottomless stomach. Appears
in Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance.

A sniper with the Greil Mercenaries. Has
a sharp tongue and is a master of the bow,
a fact that neither he nor his foes will deny.
Appears in Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance.

One of Daein's Four Riders. Wields the
Flame Lance with a callous disdain for
those around her. Appears in Fire Emblem:
Path of Radiance.

A knight with the Greil Mercenaries. Easily
excited, he flirts with women at every turn
but suffers rejection just as often. Appears
in Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance.

Effectively gets Atk+17 and can make

Acting alone, he gets Atk+12 and can
counterattack at any range. His skills
put his Special cooldown count at 1.

Can slow his foe's Special trigger and
